ygData.messageBody:
Well I've just joined, saw the last digest for areas near Freeport, but was
wondering what are good areas to hunt near Kelethin. Sure Crushbone is
there but generally jerks also. Steamfont would be great but the mino hero
has a tendency to roam around and hurt me before I can run in time. I've
heard of Dagnor's, but also heard it's slightly barren. Chessboard in BB,
well, tired of wizards kill stealing while me, or my group takes all the
damage. Basically just want any information you can give, or should I think
about moving to Freeport?

Bryne
Songweaver
